<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>io.github.aretedriver.ArgusOverview</id>
  <name>Argus Overview</name>
  <summary>Professional multi-boxing tool for EVE Online on Linux</summary>
  <metadata_license>MIT</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>

  <description>
    <p>
      Argus Overview is the complete professional multi-boxing solution for EVE Online
      that provides live window previews, team management, layout presets, broadcast
      hotkeys, and EVE settings synchronization.
    </p>
    <p>Key features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Live window previews at configurable FPS (1-60)</li>
      <li>Broadcast hotkeys - send keystrokes to all EVE windows</li>
      <li>Preview filter - quick search by character name</li>
      <li>Keyboard window control (1-9 keys)</li>
      <li>System tray integration with minimize-to-tray</li>
      <li>One-click import of all EVE windows</li>
      <li>Auto-discovery of new EVE clients</li>
      <li>Per-character global hotkeys</li>
      <li>Character and team management</li>
      <li>Layout presets with auto-tiling (2x2, 3x1, Main+Sides, etc.)</li>
      <li>Visual activity alerts (red flash detection)</li>
      <li>EVE settings synchronization between characters</li>
      <li>Multi-monitor support</li>
      <li>Low power mode for background operation</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

